title: Garmin TruSwing Club Swing Sensor
description: Want to improve your golf swing? Watch how the easy-to-use Garmin TruSwing club sensor can integrate with compatible Approach series golf GPS devices and compatible smartphones to help you see how your swing mechanics affect ball flight and shot results. With TruSwing you can analyze club head tempo, speed, swing path, face angle, and other useful metrics to help improve your overall consistency – so you can drive the ball with more control and land more shots closer to the pin.
